cross: Sarcochilus Kulnura Harrow × Sarcochilus Kulnura Sprint

measurements.description: Two hundred seventy flowers and 63 buds on 21 evenly presented upright up to 23-cm inflorescences; 45-cm wide by 30-cm high plant grown in bark and perlite mix in a 7-cm square plastic pot; sepals and petals ovate, cream heavily overlaid dark burgundy, spotted darker burgundy; lip saccate, yellow, blotched red; column white, anther cap light yellow; substance medium; texture diamond dust; also received an HCC, award #20255282.
